snippet.title: Therizinosaurus Dinosaur King USA Release Arcade Game  恐竜キング
snippet.description:
#demul #dinosaurking #arcadegame #古代王者恐竜キング

Hello guys. I'm glad I can run this game finally on emulator called demul. I haven't played this game since 2010. I hope you enjoy it!!!

There will be new videos with different dinos based on people's requests:
Every Sunday: Dinosaur King Arcade Game D-Team VS Alpha Fortress
Every Saturday: Dinosaur King Awaken Arcade Game

Also Subscribe to keep updated with new Dinosaur King videos

Wanna request too? Easy!
1. Subscribe to my channel
2. Request via Instagram, Youtube, or Email me at : 
maeve.althea@gmail.com
3. Request what dino you want me to play
4. Request the game mode
5. Don't forget to request what moves your dinos want to learn
6. Wait for your videos (as long as I reply "OK", your request is already noted)

TIPS:
- the faster you request the faster your video will be published
- request different dinos from my uploads has bigger chance to be published earlier
- LIMIT ONE REQUEST perVIDEO

- You can also request dino drawings ;) -

Dinosaur King Fansite:
https://dinosaurking.fandom.com/wiki/

My Dinosaur King Gameplay playlist
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL86ZuzAHcIs75o5l0E_Z2ln0SVa0MPOCe
( private videos = soon will be published )

Support me on:
Instagram :
https://www.instagram.com/maevealtzzz/

https://www.instagram.com/mv96_artandfilm/ ( PORTFOLIOs ONLY )

Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmzqkWAtBIpLAfQaTLeN_3Q

See ya...

#dinosaur #dino #dreamcast #chomp #amargavortex #shockwavedk

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Mv96 A.K.A (Maeve Althea) is a channel where games, arts, and movies become one.

My Channel is all about giving you My Game Walktroughs, presenting My Arts, and also Entertaining you with Animated Movies.

So, if you are a Game lover, Art enthusiasts, or Movie addict, make sure to subscribe my channel right now.

As you can see, my channel publishes videos that focus on Various Gameplays, Drawings and Paintings, and Animated Movies

If that sounds like something that could help your Drawing skill and Entertain you with my Gameplays and Movies then make sure to join me by subscribing!

Maeve Althea - "When Games, Art, and Movies become one" -

See ya...

#dinosaur #dino #dreamcast #chomp
